(439, 1, '2024-08-13 04:36:04', '2024-08-13 04:36:04', '<h2>About us:\n</h2>				\n		Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL) aims to transform the urban transportation landscape in the historic city of Patna. With a vision to create a sustainable, efficient and convenient Mass Rapid Transit System, PMRCL is dedicated to providing world-class metro services that meet the needs of our citizens and improve the overall quality of life in the region.\n					<h2>Our Mission:\n</h2>				\n		Our primary & foremost goal is to build a state-of-the-art metro network in Patna that provides seamless connectivity, reduces traffic congestion, and promotes environment friendly commuting options. We aim to provide safe, reliable and affordable transport solutions to the city\'s residents, daily commuters and visitors.\n					<h2>Key Goals:\n</h2>				\n									<h3>\n							Urban Development: 						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						PMRCL aims to contribute in the rapid urban development of Patna by providing an efficient & economical public transportation system that promotes smart growth and reduces the city\'s carbon footprint.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Customer-centric approach: 						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						we prioritize the need and comfort of our passengers and ensure that every ride in the Patna Metro having a pleasant and picturesque experience. From state of the art, air-conditioned metro cars to aristocratic stations, our focus is to meet the expectations of our valued passengers.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Sustainability and Environmental Responsibility:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						As part of our commitment to sustainability, we actively implement environment friendly practices in our operations. By encouraging the use of public transit, we seek to reduce the city\'s dependence on private transportation, thereby mitigating our environmental impact.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Safety and Security: 						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						Safety is our top priority. We adhere to strict safety measures and use the state-of-the-art technology to ensure the well-being of our passengers. Our competent & skilled staff works tirelessly to create a safe environment throughout our metro network.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Employment and Skills Development:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						PMRCL prides itself on its role as a begetter of employment opportunities. By promoting skill development, we help to improve the employability of local populace.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Technological Advancement:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						We rely on technological innovations to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of our metro services. From advanced signaling systems to user-friendly applications, we are committed to leveraging the latest advancements for the benefit of our valued passengers.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Transparency and Accountability:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						PMRCL operates with the utmost transparency and accountability. We value the trust that our stakeholders place in us and ensure that our decision-making processes are open, fair and in line with the best practices in corporate governance.					</p>\n		<p>Together with the support of the Government, our dedicated team, and the people of Patna, we are committed to building a world-class metro network that will not only serve the city\'s growing population, but also act as a catalyst for economic development and social progress.</p><p>Thank you for choosing Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited as your preferred mode of transportation. Let us embark together on a journey to a greener, better connected and prosperous Patna.</p><p>If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us. We are here to serve you better.</p>', 'about', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2025-05-16 12:04:53', '2025-05-16 12:04:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=439', 0, 