ur passengers. Our competent & skilled staff works tirelessly to create a safe environment throughout our metro network.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Employment and Skills Development:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						PMRCL prides itself on its role as a begetter of employment opportunities. By promoting skill development, we help to improve the employability of local populace.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Technological Advancement:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						We rely on technological innovations to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of our metro services. From advanced signaling systems to user-friendly applications, we are committed to leveraging the latest advancements for the benefit of our valued passengers.					</p>\n									<h3>\n							Transparency and Accountability:						\n					</h3>\n									<p>\n						PMRCL operates with the utmost transparency and accountability. We value the trust that our stakeholders place in us and ensure that our decision-making processes are open, fair and in line with the best practices in corporate governance.					</p>\n		<p>Together with the support of the Government, our dedicated team, and the people of Patna, we are committed to building a world-class metro network that will not only serve the city\'s growing population, but also act as a catalyst for economic development and social progress.</p><p>Thank you for choosing Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited as your preferred mode of transportation. Let us embark together on a journey to a greener, better connected and prosperous Patna.</p><p>If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us. We are here to serve you better.</p>', 'about', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '439-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-16 11:59:49', '2025-05-16 11:59:49', '', 439, 'http://localhost/wordpressdca/?p=1842', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
