(193, 'Together with the support of the Government, our dedicated team, and the people of Patna, we are committed to building a world-class metro network that will not only serve the city&#8217;s growing population, but also act as a catalyst for economic development and social progress.'),
(194, 'Thank you for choosing Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited as your preferred mode of transportation. Let us embark together on a journey to a greener, better connected and prosperous Patna.'),
